 range of financial, industrial,\nscientific and social settings. Examples are presented that show the nature of\nthese processes from a tutorial perspective.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2019 04:13:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Feb 2020 19:49:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-11"}
