s of 2D RD-SOC and 1D RD-SOC are discussed. It is shown that the system\nfavors novel spin textures and skyrmion configurations including an exotic\nskyrmion-half-skyrmion lattice (skyrmion-meron lattice), a complicated meron\nlattice, a skyrmion chain, and a Bloch domain wall.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2019 14:34:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-28"}
