controllers. In particular, the parallel\nimplementation on the octa-core RISC-V platform reaches a speedup of 22x and a\n69% reduction in energy consumption with respect to a single-core\nimplementation on Cortex-M4 for continuous real-time classification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Nov 2019 15:14:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Feb 2020 19:01:22 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 17 Feb 2022 11:11:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-18"}
